title: Sidewall, 1885–95
creditline: Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt
description: End of a roll, giving complete width. Long-tailed birds, in flight and perched on slender branching stems bearing small leaves, flowers and stalks of seed pods. Printed in gray and white on blue ribbed ground.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, 1885–95.
1885–95. Machine-printed on textured paper. Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt. 1931-45-122.
